&lt;h3 id="what-is-a-wallboard"&gt;What is a wallboard?&lt;a class="headerlink" href="#what-is-a-wallboard" title="Permanent link"&gt;&amp;para;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A wallboard is a type of information radiator that displays vital data about the progress of the development team. Similar to a scoreboard at a sporting event, wallboards are large, highly visible and easy to understand for anyone walking&amp;nbsp;by.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Traditional wallboards are made of paper or use sticky notes on a wall. Electronic wallboards are very effective since they update automatically with real-time data ensuring that people check back&amp;nbsp;regularly.&lt;/p&gt;
